data.description: Gorgeous Home in Premier Location. The sellers have done an incredible job making this a Dream Home with approx. $200,000 in UPGRADES! You willfeel like you stepped into PARADISE with the EXTRA Large Cul-De-Sac Lot with an AMAZING Professionally Landscaped Back Yard. Downstairs youwill find the Living Room, Dining Room, Family Room plus a Guest Bedroom and Bathroom. Perfect for Entertaining! Remodeled Kitchen hasStainless Steel Appliances, Granite & Upgraded Maple Cabinets. Laminate Flooring, 5.5'' Baseboards, & Plantation Shutters throughout. ALL bathrooms have been Upgraded with Tile Showers, Granite Counters, & Flooring. Brand New State of the Art Water System. Garage with Service  Door, Cabinets, Epoxy Floors, Extra Insulation & Workbench. Spectacular Backyard with Gated Pool.
